They're fast. They're flavorful. And they're right at your fingertips. The 50 Best Vegan Recipes is an appetizing selection of delicious dishes that'll give you plenty of meat- and dairy-free options. From Sweet & Spicy Cucumber Salad to Butternut Squash Soup, there's plenty included so you can whip up satisfying and tasty snacks and meals. Enjoy!
